Finally, our implementation of Ford-Fulkerson:
``` :results :true :display :true :code
(defn ford-fulkerson [G a b]
   (loop [H G S {}]
     (let [R (find-a-path H a b)]
       (if (empty? R)
         (into {} S)
         (let [v (reduce min (map H R))
               P (zipmap R (repeat v))]
           (recur (residual-graph H P) (merge-with + S P)))))))
```
